&lt;h1&gt;Use git to publish&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A very good startup:&lt;a href="http://frantic1048.com/blog/bo-ke-dan-sheng-ji-ji-yu-githubpelicanchuang-jian-bo-ke-de-zheng-ge-guo-cheng.html"&gt;http://frantic1048.com/blog/bo-ke-dan-sheng-ji-ji-yu-githubpelicanchuang-jian-bo-ke-de-zheng-ge-guo-cheng.html&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
